Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0250,,#23 停转世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:48.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托付…给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥 米迦哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这搭载在Gundam上的功能是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda数据中没有相关资料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是预先载入GN Drive的黑匣子里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 Veda中Meister们的数据似乎被彻底删除了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格连我变更计划都预测到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以神自居的理想主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要耍弄我们到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:17.68,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}拉格朗日1 资源卫星群
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭用集装箱 开始连接到托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾部推进器 收纳完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在敌人打过来之前完成整备 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将机体中积蓄的高浓度压缩粒子全面释放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一定时间内获得将性能提高三倍的功率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有原型太阳炉才有的机能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM系统
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚老爹还给我们留下这么好的礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:02:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 使用TRANS-AM之后 机体性能会急剧下降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓双刃剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那发来的密信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 收到返回托勒密的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有要件报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面上的拟造太阳炉搭载型MS 全部上了宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 一架Gundam Throne被敌方俘获
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘获？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是联合国军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取Throne的机师 是阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把人耍到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是补给先结束 还是联合国军先来犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 都得在拉格朗日1打一仗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.93,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}联合国军 维吉尼亚级大型运输舰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然专门准备了备用零件 够省心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你俘获这架Gundam的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是顶武特种部队的瑟尔盖·史米卢佐夫中校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙俄罗斯的荒熊亲自来打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是法国第4独立外籍骑兵联队的盖利·比亚吉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特来参加Gundam讨伐作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺想听听看 你是如何俘获Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是商业机密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离可视战斗宙域 还有2000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 第一战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部队准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一刻终于来了 哈瓦德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 离可视战斗宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到答案了吗 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们 收到了伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格的托付
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:04:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我会以自己的意志 为根除战争而战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Gundam一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我可没觉得我们能够做到根除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们这些愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论好坏 都会铭刻在人们心中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我才开始思考 「天人」…我们 到底有什么存在的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类只对自己亲身经历过的事物 才能从真正意义上理解它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 捕捉到联合国军的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近中的敌方运输舰 推测为UNION的维吉尼亚级 数量三架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离可视战斗区域 还有4200
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用资源卫星 托勒密后退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios Virtue 准备防卫战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 在托勒密内待机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 别这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做是不是强硬了点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用说的他可不会听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在上次战斗中被他所救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这次就由我来保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 固定到电磁领域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 阿勒路亚·哈普提森 开始迎击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方运输舰中有MS出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 提耶利亚·艾迪 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:06:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方MS为拟GN Drive搭载型 26架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方MS部队中发现Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告所有机师 出击的Gundam只有两架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用245阵型应战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用包围战歼灭之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 请期待我的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~ 哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位真起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先发制人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新装备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用尾部推进器提高机动性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 阵型别打乱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按E计划各个击破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击无效
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ Throne吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉它 Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验体E57
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·比利斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 尾部推进器破损
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和疑似超兵的MS交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 正遭到敌方MS的集中性攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Gundam下达撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥 能听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GN-Armer进行对舰攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你的战术办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉要你陪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头…头疼消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波被我屏蔽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了他们 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T…TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新武器吗
